netfilter: Kconfig: use 'default y' instead of 'm' for bool config option

This option, NF_CONNTRACK_SECMARK, is a bool, so it can never be 'm'.

Fixes: 33b8e77605620 ("[NETFILTER]: Add CONFIG_NETFILTER_ADVANCED option")
